# ── the-team skill — .gitignore ───────────────────────────────────────────────

# IMPORTANT: the Kiro steering files under kiro/.kiro/steering/ are part of this
# repo's deliverable. Do NOT ignore them. Many "Kiro" gitignore templates treat
# .kiro/ as local IDE config and ignore it — that would drop the whole Kiro
# variant here. The rule below force-keeps it.
!kiro/.kiro/
!kiro/.kiro/steering/
!kiro/.kiro/steering/*.md

# ── Secrets — never commit ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The research workflow (NotebookLM MCP, optional headroom, any API use) involves
# Google auth and tokens. None of that belongs in version control.
.env
.env.*
*.local
*.pem
*.key
credentials.json
token.json
client_secret*.json
**/secrets/

# ── Build artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The distributable zips are generated, not source. Regenerate from the tracked
# files instead of committing them.
*.zip
dist/
build/

# ── Node (only if you run the design.md linter or notebooklm-mcp locally) ─────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# ── Python (only if you run headroom or a Python MCP locally) ─────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/

# ── Editor / IDE local config (NOT the kiro/ deliverable above) ───────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── OS junk ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── Logs / temp ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.tmp
.cache/
